# .env is intentionally committed for Lovable Cloud production builds.
# It must contain ONLY frontend-safe VITE_SUPABASE_* public values (URL, PUBLISHABLE_KEY, PROJECT_ID).
# Never add SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY, DB passwords/URLs, JWT secrets, or any private keys here.

